  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>steaks </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let them adjust to room temperature</p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Slice the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into discs, approx. 1cm thick</p><p>Slice the <strong>parsnips</strong> (skins on) into discs, approx. 1cm thick</p><p>Peel and cut the <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641305767794-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641305767794-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641305767794-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641305767794-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1641305767794-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> potato discs</strong>, <strong>parsnip discs</strong> and <strong>onion wedges</strong> to a baking tray, drizzle<strong> </strong>with <strong>olive oil </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 20 min</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641305772271-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641305772271-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641305772271-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641305772271-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1641305772271-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate (don't chop) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>dried sage</strong>, <strong>grated garlic </strong>and <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a small bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>sage crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1641305775618-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1641305775618-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1641305775618-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1641305775618-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1641305775618-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>pork loin steaks</strong> with the<strong> sage crumb</strong></p><p>Tip: Press the crumb into the pork steaks firmly with your hands to help it stick!</p><p>Once the veg has had 20 min, add the <strong>sage-crusted pork steaks</strong> to the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a final 13-15 min or until the crumb is golden and the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641305779568-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641305779568-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641305779568-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641305779568-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1641305779568-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash the <strong>spring greens</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Shredded-spring-greens-1676659889653-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Shredded-spring-greens-1676659889653-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Shredded-spring-greens-1676659889653-x700.jpg",
