          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Shredded-spring-greens-1676659889653-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> pieces of <strong>tin foil</strong> approx. the size of an A3 sheet of paper and layer them over each other</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced spring greens</strong> to the middle with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Scrunch the edges of the foil around the greens to form 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> sealed parcel<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> and add to a baking tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 10-12 min or until the greens are tender</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1641305787144-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1641305787144-x400.jpg",
